        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-77eff999-601d-4dab-856f-831b73f715aa">
                The Prime Minister
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-77eff999-601d-4dab-856f-831b73f715aa" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-06-17/debates/492b49aa-a07c-4466-b385-64cf6dfc1ecd/Nato(PoliticalPronouncements)#contribution-77eff999-601d-4dab-856f-831b73f715aa">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">The right hon. Gentleman, in his tenure of office, found himself thoroughly able to keep a most active political life going in combination with his duties as Defence Minister.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-77eff999-601d-4dab-856f-831b73f715aa" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-06-17/debates/492b49aa-a07c-4466-b385-64cf6dfc1ecd/Nato(PoliticalPronouncements)#contribution-77eff999-601d-4dab-856f-831b73f715aa">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
